{"tid":388184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Clean the window go outside","createTime":"2017-09-05T09:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T09:27:14.000Z","uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f71c1c1965a0243b0caf262fd12c66aceedc69a6","tid":388184,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"黃埔花園男子墮樓亡　疑抹窗時失足 (15:49)<br />\n<br />\n紅磡黃埔花園9期百合苑，下午1時許，一名50多歲男子，被人發現倒臥於大廈對開的花槽，昏迷不醒。救護員接報到場，將他送院搶救，最終證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，發現死者所住的單位窗戶打開，窗戶有毛巾、清潔劑等物品，不排除他抹窗時失足墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170905/s00001/1504595658204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170905%2Fs00001%2F1504595658204&d=AA1KCNrHYCdSNSZN7dlTNghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5a27c392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170905%2Fs00001%2F1504595658204&h=4c98ed6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170905/s00001/1504595658204</a>"}]}